trans-unit.source: Defines identifiers for the standard set of commands that are available to most applications.
trans-unit.target: Define os identificadores para o conjunto padrão de comandos disponíveis para a maioria dos aplicativos.

trans-unit.source: This class defines <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> identifiers for standard commands that are available to designers.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe define <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> identificadores de comandos padrão que estão disponíveis para designers.

trans-unit.source: To add a command from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands> class to a designer menu, you must call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> method of an <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> and add a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> that contains a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> from <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands>.
trans-unit.target: Para adicionar um comando do <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands> classe para um menu designer, você deve chamar o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService.AddCommand%2A> método de um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService> e adicione um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> que contém um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands>.

trans-unit.source: The following code example illustrates how to add a member of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands> class to a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> and how to add the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> to an <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo de código a seguir ilustra como adicionar um membro do <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands> de classe para um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> e como adicionar o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.MenuCommand> para um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IMenuCommandService>.

trans-unit.source: for full access to system resources.
trans-unit.target: Para obter acesso completo aos recursos do sistema.

Gets the first of a set of verbs.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o primeiro de um conjunto de verbos.

trans-unit.source: This field is read-only.
This is a special <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> that identifies the first of a set of designer verbs.
trans-unit.target: Este é um especial <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> que identifica a primeira de um conjunto de verbos do designer.

trans-unit.source: The Visual Studio Windows Forms Designer automatically maps designer verbs to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A> property on <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, so generally you do not need to access this command.
trans-unit.target: O Visual Studio Windows Forms Designer mapeia automaticamente os verbos do designer para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner.Verbs%2A> propriedade <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesigner>, geralmente você não precisa acessar esse comando.

trans-unit.source: All designer verbs for an object become commands with a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> within a sequential range of IDs that begins with <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbFirst> and ends with <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbLast>.
trans-unit.target: Todos os verbos do designer de um objeto tornam-se comandos com um <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.CommandID> dentro de um sequencial intervalo de IDs que começa com <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbFirst> e termina com <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.StandardCommands.VerbLast>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the last of a set of verbs.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o último de um conjunto de verbos.
